_text = "I walked to the deepest part in the tunnel. On either side of me, I can see a memory looking back at me.\n\nOn my left, I see my parents. Before they got divorced. They look happy, but an uneasy feeling floats between them.\n\nOn my right, I see a collection of memories tied to certain people. I see my greatest friends, and how I lost them in my own mistakes. I see them smiling at me as well, but I can sense the absence between us.\n\nDo I go left or right?"

roomInit(blackSprite, _text, Monitor, MonitorNo, MonitorYes, ParentsSittingMemory, GroupPhotoMmeory, false)
